<title>习近平率中央代表团抵达拉萨出席西藏自治区成立60周年庆祝活动</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9B%A2%E6%8A%B5%E8%BE%BE%E6%8B%89%E8%90%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%BA%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B60%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%86%E7%A5%9D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8</link>
